00:48:50.802 --> 00:48:51.929
great.

744
00:48:54.723 --> 00:48:56.391
You don't exactly sound thrilled.

745
00:48:57.935 --> 00:48:59.478
Oh. uh...

746
00:49:00.687 --> 00:49:04.149
I... I just... I don't know
how long this is sustainable.

747
00:49:05.359 --> 00:49:06.526
Do we really
want to try and find

748
00:49:06.610 --> 00:49:08.487
somewhere safe
to sleep every night?

749
00:49:09.446 --> 00:49:11.698
Hasn't worked out lately.

750
00:49:11.782 --> 00:49:14.326
What is going on
right now. Mads?

751
00:49:18.038 --> 00:49:19.665
You haven't even put
your ring on yet.

752
00:49:20.791 --> 00:49:22.125
GREGORY PECK: <i>(OVER SPEAKER)
Suits you.</i>

753
00:49:22.209 --> 00:49:23.710
<i>You should always wear my clothes.</i>

754
00:49:23.794 --> 00:49:25.796
AUDREY HEPBURN: <i>Seems I do.</i>

755
00:49:28.548 --> 00:49:31.760
MADDIE: It's not that
I don't love you.

756
00:49:31.843 --> 00:49:33.178
I do. I love you.

757
00:49:34.388 --> 00:49:35.514
I just...

758
00:49:36.181 --> 00:49:38.016
<i>(MOVIE CONTINUES INDISTINCTLY)</i>

759
00:49:38.100 --> 00:49:41.019
I... I don't love this life.

760
00:49:42.437 --> 00:49:43.689
I mean...

761
00:49:43.772 --> 00:49:45.691
you know I grew up
always being shuffled

762
00:49:45.774 --> 00:49:47.401
from one foster home
to the next.

763
00:49:47.484 --> 00:49:49.903
I never had a home home
like you did.

764
00:49:49.987 --> 00:49:51.780
You know that's not
all it's cracked up to be.

765
00:49:51.863 --> 00:49:54.241
<i>(CHUCKLES SOFTLY)</i> You see?

766
00:49:54.324 --> 00:49:56.034
The thing you're running away from

767
00:49:56.118 --> 00:49:59.329
is the very thing I've been
searching for my entire life.

768
00:50:01.164 --> 00:50:02.749
I thought this was what you wanted.

769
00:50:02.833 --> 00:50:04.835
You and me. together.

770
00:50:04.918 --> 00:50:07.295
On the open road.
Unshackled from our desks.

771
00:50:07.379 --> 00:50:08.547
MADDIE: I did. I did.

772
00:50:08.630 --> 00:50:11.174
It was fun in the beginning.
but I...

773
00:50:13.093 --> 00:50:15.512
- <i>(SIGHS)</i>
- All right. So. what. you...

774
00:50:16.555 --> 00:50:17.889
You want to slow down?

775
00:50:19.891 --> 00:50:21.184
<i>(INHALES)</i>

776
00:50:22.853 --> 00:50:24.771
I want to... <i>(SIGHS)</i>

777
00:50:24.855 --> 00:50:26.023
I want to stop.

778
00:50:32.654 --> 00:50:34.197
- You want to stop?
- Yeah.

779
00:50:41.163 --> 00:50:42.456
I'll pack up the van.

780
00:50:43.957 --> 00:50:45.584
- Sell it.
- MADDIE: No.

781
00:50:45.667 --> 00:50:47.335
<i>(SIGHS)</i> Head back to Brooklyn.

782
00:50:47.419 --> 00:50:49.129
Maybe we can get our lease back.

783
00:50:49.212 --> 00:50:50.380
Hey. look at me.

784
00:50:53.133 --> 00:50:54.843
I saw your face at the van meet.

785
00:50:56.553 --> 00:50:59.306
You love this.

786
00:51:00.348 --> 00:51:01.850
Being free.

787
00:51:03.310 --> 00:51:06.521
And I'd never ask you
to give up your dream.

788
00:51:08.440 --> 00:51:09.691
I'm just worried...

789
00:51:11.276 --> 00:51:13.653
That no matter
what direction we take...

790
00:51:13.737 --> 00:51:15.864
- one of us will end up--
- <i>(LOUD STATIC OVER SPEAKER)</i>

791
00:51:19.284 --> 00:51:20.577
<i>(STATIC STOPS)</i>

792
00:51:20.660 --> 00:51:21.828
TYLER: Just glitched out.

793
00:51:24.122 --> 00:51:26.166
But what were you saying?
One of us will end up what?

794
00:51:26.249 --> 00:51:28.043
<i>(LIGHTS FLICKER AND TURN OFF)</i>

795
00:51:30.212 --> 00:51:31.588
MADDIE: What just happened?

796
00:51:32.297 --> 00:51:33.423
TYLER: I'm not sure.

797
00:51:35.425 --> 00:51:37.302
<i>(MOVIE CONTINUES WITHOUT AUDIO)</i>

798
00:51:38.053 --> 00:51:39.179
Ty.

799
00:51:40.847 --> 00:51:42.265
What is that?

800
00:51:42.349 --> 00:51:43.475
MADDIE: I don't know. Ty.

801
00:51:54.027 --> 00:51:55.320
<i>(BREATH TREMBLING)</i>

802
00:51:55.403 --> 00:51:56.738
<i>(FLASHLIGHT CLICKS)</i>

803
00:51:56.822 --> 00:51:57.948
Stay there.

804
00:51:59.741 --> 00:52:01.159
Hey. man.

805
00:52:24.724 --> 00:52:26.059
<i>(GASPS)</i>

806
00:52:31.022 --> 00:52:32.232
<i>(GASPS)</i>

807
00:52:41.867 --> 00:52:43.326
<i>(BREATHING HEAVILY)</i>

808
00:52:46.121 --> 00:52:47.998
- You saw that. right?
- Yeah.

809
00:52:48.081 --> 00:52:49.666
- <i>(BRANCHES SNAPPING)</i>
- <i>(BREATHING HEAVILY)</i>

810
00:52:55.463 --> 00:52:57.090
- <i>(LEAVES RUSTLING)</i>
- <i>(GASPS)</i>

811
00:53:08.518 --> 00:53:10.478
- TYLER: You see anything?
- MADDIE: No.

812
00:53:11.938 --> 00:53:13.315
<i>(BRANCHES SNAPPING)</i>

813
00:53:17.402 --> 00:53:19.237
<i>(TYLER BREATHING HEAVILY)</i>

814
00:53:20.322 --> 00:53:22.240
- <i>(FOOTSTEPS RUNNING)</i>
- Oh. hell no.

815
00:53:22.324 --> 00:53:24.951
<i>(FOOTSTEPS RUNNING)</i>

816
00:53:31.917 --> 00:53:33.293
<i>(FOOTSTEPS RUNNING)</i>

817
00:53:38.131 --> 00:53:39.674
<i>(BRANCH SNAPS)</i>

818
00:53:39.758 --> 00:53:41.927
<i>(MADDIE SCREAMS)</i>

819
00:53:42.636 --> 00:53:43.803
<i>(ROARING)</i>

820
00:53:46.348 --> 00:53:48.475
- <i>(DOOR CLOSES)</i>
- <i>(MADDIE AND TYLER GASPING)</i>

821
00:53:49.059 --> 00:53:50.143
<i>(LOUD THUD)</i>

822
00:53:51.311 --> 00:53:54.731
<i>(LOUD THUDDING)</i>

823
00:53:55.232 --> 00:53:57.484
<i>(LOUD CRASHING)</i>

824
00:53:57.567 --> 00:53:58.985
<i>(VAN RATTLING)</i>

825
00:54:01.446 --> 00:54:03.782
<i>(MADDIE SCREAMING)</i>

826
00:54:03.865 --> 00:54:05.659
<i>(VAN CONTINUES RATTLING)</i>

827
00:54:12.207 --> 00:54:13.333
<i>(MADDIE WHIMPERING)</i>

828
00:54:18.046 --> 00:54:19.172
<i>(RATTLING STOPS)</i>

829
00:54:19.256 --> 00:54:22.008
<i>(BOTH BREATHING HEAVILY)</i>

830
00:54:22.092 --> 00:54:24.261
- It stopped.
- <i>(MADDIE CRIES)</i>

831
00:54:24.344 --> 00:54:25.553
It stopped.

832
00:54:26.429 --> 00:54:28.556
- We got to move.
- Yeah.

833
00:54:28.640 --> 00:54:30.016
- Come on. What?
- The keys.

834
00:54:30.100 --> 00:54:31.977
I don't have the keys. Um...

835
00:54:32.060 --> 00:54:33.186
- MADDIE: Where...
- Um...

836
00:54:34.437 --> 00:54:35.563
They're outside.

837
00:54:36.856 --> 00:54:38.233
- What?
- They got to be.

838
00:54:44.114 --> 00:54:46.157
- Careful.
- <i>(SIGHS)</i>

839
00:54:53.373 --> 00:54:54.916
<i>(PANTING)</i> Come on. Come on!

840
00:54:56.668 --> 00:54:59.087
- Come on!
- <i>(OBJECTS CLATTERING)</i>

841
00:55:07.429 --> 00:55:08.972
<i>(KEYS JANGLING)</i>

842
00:55:12.517 --> 00:55:14.060
<i>(KEYS JANGLING)</i>

843
00:55:15.020 --> 00:55:16.938
<i>(BREATHING SHAKILY)</i>

844
00:55:24.446 --> 00:55:25.864
<i>(KEYS JANGLING)</i>

845
00:55:38.168 --> 00:55:39.210
<i>(BREATH TREMBLING)</i>

846
00:55:39.294 --> 00:55:40.503
<i>(BRANCHES SNAPPING)</i>

847
00:55:53.350 --> 00:55:54.726
<i>(KEYS JANGLING)</i>

848
00:56:05.987 --> 00:56:07.405
<i>(BREATHING HEAVILY)</i>

849
00:56:40.313 --> 00:56:41.564
<i>(SCREECHING)</i>

850
00:56:41.648 --> 00:56:43.483
<i>(TYLER GASPING)</i>

851
00:56:45.985 --> 00:56:47.570
- MADDIE: Come on!
- <i>(GASPS)</i>

852
00:56:52.409 --> 00:56:53.910
Come on. come on. go!

853
00:56:54.953 --> 00:56:55.954
<i>(ENGINE STARTS)</i>

854
00:56:56.037 --> 00:56:57.080
Go. go. go!

855
00:56:57.163 --> 00:56:58.957
<i>(ENGINE REVVING)</i>

856
00:57:05.130 --> 00:57:06.714
What the fuck is going on?

857
00:57:07.882 --> 00:57:09.008
<i>(BREATH TREMBLING)</i>

858
00:57:10.218 --> 00:57:11.511
Is that what
you've been seeing?

859
00:57:22.605 --> 00:57:23.815
<i>(TIRES SCREECHING)</i>

860
00:57:28.903 --> 00:57:30.029
Come on.

861
00:57:34.576 --> 00:57:35.702
<i>(DOORBELL RINGS)</i>

862
00:57:35.785 --> 00:57:37.996
<i>(BLUES MUSIC PLAYING
OVER SPEAKERS)</i>

863
00:57:54.137 --> 00:57:55.680
TYLER: Hobo Code?

864
00:57:55.763 --> 00:57:57.265
It's the way drifters
communicated back in the day

865
00:57:57.348 --> 00:57:58.850
when the roads
were first being built.

866
00:57:59.809 --> 00:58:02.645
They used these symbols
to warn each other.

867
00:58:05.482 --> 00:58:07.233
This is on our van.

868
00:58:09.194 --> 00:58:10.945
And the car that crashed.

869
00:58:12.655 --> 00:58:13.865
This thing...

870
00:58:14.824 --> 00:58:16.910
it latches onto you
when you're on the road.

871
00:58:16.993 --> 00:58:18.912
WAITRESS: Some waters for you?

872
00:58:22.248 --> 00:58:23.333
Thank you.

873
00:58:24.834 --> 00:58:27.128
- I'll give you two a moment.
- TYLER: Mm-hmm.

874
00:58:31.382 --> 00:58:32.842
Some people call him...

875
00:58:33.927 --> 00:58:35.345
the Passenger.

876
00:58:37.222 --> 00:58:40.266
He made that guy crash.

877
00:58:41.226 --> 00:58:42.602
And then we stopped.

878
00:58:43.811 --> 00:58:45.146
And somehow

879
00:58:45.230 --> 00:58:46.981
everywhere we've gone...

880
00:58:47.482 --> 00:58:48.858
he's there.

881
00:58:48.942 --> 00:58:50.443
There's got to be a way
we can shake him.

882
00:58:51.277 --> 00:58:52.445
<i>(ENGINE STARTS)</i>

883
00:58:54.072 --> 00:58:55.406
He marked the van.

884
00:58:56.241 --> 00:58:57.283
Mads. look at me.

885
00:58:57.367 --> 00:58:58.993
He marked the van. right?

886
00:58:59.702 --> 00:59:00.828
Right?

887
00:59:01.996 --> 00:59:04.415
So we just dump it. yeah?

888
00:59:04.499 --> 00:59:05.833
MADDIE: No.

889
00:59:05.917 --> 00:59:07.252
- We burn the van.
- No. no.

890
00:59:07.335 --> 00:59:09.045
I don't think
it works like that.

891
00:59:10.004 --> 00:59:11.172
From what I read...

892
00:59:12.340 --> 00:59:13.716
it's not the van he's marked.

893
00:59:15.969 --> 00:59:17.178
It's us.

894
00:59:17.262 --> 00:59:18.513
No.

895
00:59:20.348 --> 00:59:23.142
No. No. we can shake him.

896
00:59:25.979 --> 00:59:28.773
<i>(MADDIE BREATHING HEAVILY)</i>

897
00:59:29.732 --> 00:59:31.276
- I'll be right back.
- Yeah.

898
00:59:31.985 --> 00:59:33.236
Yeah.

899
00:59:40.118 --> 00:59:42.370
<i>(BREATHING HEAVILY)</i>

900
00:59:50.128 --> 00:59:51.421
<i>(WATER RUNNING)</i>

901
00:59:51.504 --> 00:59:53.631
<i>(WHIMPERING)</i>

902
01:00:05.977 --> 01:00:07.520
<i>(BREATHING HEAVILY)</i>

903
01:00:28.124 --> 01:00:29.709
MADDIE: Hey. Hey.

904
01:00:29.792 --> 01:00:31.210
Uh...

905
01:00:31.294 --> 01:00:32.503
We need to find Diane.

906
01:00:33.421 --> 01:00:35.882
- Who?
- The nomad from the van meet.

907
01:00:36.799 --> 01:00:38.843
She tried to warn me about this.

908
01:00:38.926 --> 01:00:40.053
What do you know about her?

909
01:00:40.136 --> 01:00:42.138
She was headed to Flagstaff

910
01:00:42.221 --> 01:00:44.807
to work in a seafood restaurant.

911
01:00:44.891 --> 01:00:46.225
There can't be many of those.

912
01:00:47.101 --> 01:00:49.062
Flagstaff is a straight shot
from here.

913
01:00:49.145 --> 01:00:50.605
- Let's go.
- No.

914
01:00:50.688 --> 01:00:52.106
She said not to drive at night.

915
01:00:53.483 --> 01:00:54.484
We should wait.

916
01:00:54.567 --> 01:00:55.943
<i>(ENGINE STARTS)</i>

917
01:01:28.267 --> 01:01:29.727
<i>(MEDALLION CLINKING)</i>

918
01:01:32.855 --> 01:01:35.733
TYLER: <i>(EXHALES)</i>
We're running out of daylight.

919
01:01:35.817 --> 01:01:38.653
- How much further?
- We should be close.

920
01:01:38.736 --> 01:01:41.906
Manager at the restaurant
said she was staying here.

921
01:01:41.989 --> 01:01:44.283
- <i>(TIRE BLOWS OUT)</i>
- TYLER: Shit!

922
01:01:45.118 --> 01:01:46.327
MADDIE: We can't stop.

923
01:01:46.786 --> 01:01:47.870
TYLER: I know.

924
01:01:48.663 --> 01:01:49.997
But we haven't got a choice.

925
01:02:01.259 --> 01:02:03.136
This thing only comes out
at dark. right?

926
01:02:04.429 --> 01:02:05.888
So either we wait around...

927
01:02:07.598 --> 01:02:09.183
or we get out there
and deal with this.

928
01:02:09.851 --> 01:02:11.561
<i>(SIGHS)</i> We'll make it quick.

929
01:02:17.358 --> 01:02:19.068
<i>(TOOL SQUEAKING)</i>

930
01:02:22.113 --> 01:02:23.990
<i>(TYLER GRUNTING)</i>

931
01:02:33.166 --> 01:02:35.084
- <i>(TOOL SQUEAKING)</i>
- <i>(TYLER GRUNTING)</i>

932
01:02:41.382 --> 01:02:42.633
<i>(LEAVES RUSTLING)</i>

933
01:02:45.803 --> 01:02:47.430
<i>(TYLER SIGHING)</i> Oh. yes.

934
01:02:48.014 --> 01:02:50.224
<i>(TYLER GRUNTING)</i>

935
01:03:00.318 --> 01:03:01.611
<i>(TIRE THUDS)</i>

936
01:03:07.450 --> 01:03:08.576
<i>(SOFTLY)</i> What the fuck?

937
01:03:11.078 --> 01:03:12.371
Hey.

938
01:03:13.039 --> 01:03:14.165
- Baby!
- Yeah.

939
01:03:14.248 --> 01:03:16.042
- TYLER: Light.
- Oh. Sorry.

940
01:03:18.211 --> 01:03:20.379
- TYLER: The bolt things...
- They were here. right?

941
01:03:21.255 --> 01:03:23.257
Where'd they go?
They were just here.

942
01:03:23.341 --> 01:03:25.301
Here. give me.
Give me the light.

943
01:03:30.640 --> 01:03:32.266
- Oh. you got to be kidding me.
- Anything?

944
01:03:34.977 --> 01:03:36.604
- Careful.
- <i>(TYLER GRUNTS)</i>

945
01:03:38.105 --> 01:03:39.524
<i>(BRANCHES SNAPPING)</i>

946
01:03:41.150 --> 01:03:42.193
<i>(SOFT THUD)</i>

947
01:03:42.276 --> 01:03:43.528
<i>(METAL CREAKING)</i>

948
01:03:47.406 --> 01:03:49.659
- <i>(BREATHING HEAVILY)</i>
- <i>(PARKING LIGHTS FLICKERING)</i>

949
01:03:51.828 --> 01:03:53.037
<i>(TYLER GRUNTS)</i>

950
01:04:05.174 --> 01:04:07.468
<i>(SQUEAKING)</i>

951
01:04:07.552 --> 01:04:09.637
<i>(CREAKING)</i>

952
01:04:18.229 --> 01:04:19.814
<i>(METAL CREAKING)</i>

953
01:04:27.154 --> 01:04:28.281
TYLER: Think I got them all.

954
01:04:34.203 --> 01:04:35.705
<i>(DOOR CREAKING)</i>

955
01:04:45.214 --> 01:04:46.757
<i>(PARKING LIGHTS
FLICKERING SLOWLY)</i>

956
01:04:51.137 --> 01:04:52.346
<i>(GASPS)</i>

957
01:05:01.689 --> 01:05:02.857
<i>(MADDIE SCREAMING)</i>

958
01:05:05.026 --> 01:05:06.193
TYLER: Maddie?

959
01:05:07.820 --> 01:05:10.031
- Maddie!
- <i>(SCREAMING)</i>

960
01:05:12.575 --> 01:05:14.243
<i>(VAN CREAKING)</i>

961
01:05:14.327 --> 01:05:16.621
<i>(GROANING)</i> Ah!

962
01:05:16.704 --> 01:05:19.624
<i>(CREAKING CONTINUES)</i>

963
01:05:26.213 --> 01:05:28.090
- <i>(FLESH SQUELCHES)</i>
- <i>(SCREAMING)</i>

964
01:05:28.966 --> 01:05:31.427
<i>(GROANING IN PAIN)</i>

965
01:05:34.388 --> 01:05:35.806
<i>(GRUNTS)</i>

966
01:05:37.683 --> 01:05:38.809
<i>(SQUELCHING)</i>

967
01:05:40.645 --> 01:05:42.229
<i>(GROANING)</i>

968
01:05:44.231 --> 01:05:45.775
<i>(PANTING)</i>

969
01:05:48.569 --> 01:05:50.446
Okay. Maddie. <i>(GRUNTS)</i>

970
01:05:51.322 --> 01:05:53.074
<i>(PANTING)</i>

971
01:05:55.785 --> 01:05:56.911
Maddie!

972
01:06:06.420 --> 01:06:08.464
<i>(GRUNTING)</i>

973
01:06:10.216 --> 01:06:11.717
<i>(PANTING)</i>

974
01:06:18.724 --> 01:06:19.850
Come on.

975
01:06:21.268 --> 01:06:22.603
Come on!

976
01:06:25.272 --> 01:06:27.608
<i>(GASPS. PANTING)</i>

977
01:07:12.611 --> 01:07:14.363
<i>(BRAKES SCREECH)</i>

978
01:07:15.740 --> 01:07:17.074
Ty?

979
01:07:17.158 --> 01:07:19.285
- TYLER: Maddie! Oh. my God.
- Oh. Oh. my...

980
01:07:19.368 --> 01:07:20.953
<i>(TYLER BREATHING HEAVILY)</i>

981
01:07:22.538 --> 01:07:23.664
Oh. my God.

982
01:07:25.332 --> 01:07:26.667
I thought I lost you. baby.

983
01:07:30.212 --> 01:07:31.338
It's okay.

984
01:07:32.381 --> 01:07:33.382
<i>(IN DEMONIC VOICE)</i> It's over.

985
01:07:37.178 --> 01:07:38.429
<i>(EVIL LAUGHTER)</i>

